<ul>
<li class='cover' id='bookCover_2052'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2052.The_Big_Sleep"><img alt="The Big Sleep (Philip Marlowe #1)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1371584712l/2052._SX98_.jpg" />
